==English==
===Pronunciation===
/ˈveəriəbəl/, /<tt>"ve@ri@b@l</tt>/
===Adjective===
'''variable'''

# Liable to [[vary]].

===Noun===
# (mathematics) In Algebra, it is a letter that represents an unspecefied and/or unknown quantity.
